        <h3>Who we are</h3>
        <div class="padded-contents">
            <p>The Student Advice Service is part of the Oxford University Student Union. The Service is staffed by two part time qualified and experienced permanent Advisors.</p>
            <h4>Lisa Stokes-King</h4>
            <p>Lisa is a part time permanent Student Advisor and has been working for the Service since 2009. She has been an Oxford undergraduate, a graduate, an international student and a mature student. She also has related experience of being a parent while studying.</p>
            <h4>Cate Hemingway</h4>
            <p>Cate is a part time permanent Student Advisor who studied at Cambridge and Oxford. Cate has experience working as an assistant junior dean and MCR President at both Oxford and Cambridge. Cate is a qualified and registered social worker and psychologist.</p>
        </div>
