    <div class="card">
        <h3>Better Lives</h3>
        <div class="padded-contents">
            <p>The Student Advice Service is a FREE, safe, and confidential advice and information service available to all Oxford University students. We are independent from the Colleges and the University, and we are here to give support to students that are facing difficult situations.</p>
            <p>Advisors have experience dealing with the following areas:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Accommodation</li>
                <li>Academic Appeals</li>
                <li>Bullying and Harassment</li>
                <li>College Discipline</li>
                <li>Disability</li>
                <li>Finance</li>
                <li>Graduate issues (transfer status and supervisor issues)</li>
                <li>Health and Mental Health</li>
                <li>Student Parenting</li>
                <li>Sexual Health</li>
                <li>General Welfare</li>
            </ul>
            <p>However, advisors are happy to find the answer to any query you might have, however trivial it might seem.</p>
        </div>
